SESSIONS
 
Ctrl+A, shift+C     New session (prompts for name)
Ctrl+A, )           Next session
Ctrl+A, (           Previous session
Ctrl+A, $           Rename session
Ctrl+A, s           List sessions
Ctrl+A, Shift+X     Kill session
 
 
WINDOWS
 
Ctrl+A, c           New window
Ctrl+A, n           Next window
Ctrl+A, p           Previous window
Ctrl+A, 1-9         Jump to window 1-9
Ctrl+A, l           Toggle between last two windows
Ctrl+A, , (comma)   Rename window
Ctrl+A, w           List windows
 
 
PANES
 
Ctrl+A, |           Split horizontal
Ctrl+A, -           Split vertical
Alt+Arrow           Switch pane in direction
Ctrl+A, Space       Automatic layout
Ctrl+A, {           Swap with previous pane
Ctrl+A, }           Swap with next pane
Ctrl+A, x           Close pane (or exit the shell)
 
 
MISCELLANEOUS
 
Ctrl+A, PageUp/Dn   Scroll (or use mouse wheel; Esc to return)
Ctrl+A, d           Disconnect
 
 
HELP
 
Ctrl+A, h           Display this cheat sheet (Esc to return)
Ctrl+A, ?           Display all key bindings (Esc to return)
